## § 6. Follow Writer (from article page — no navigation needed)

🚨 **MANDATORY after every engagement (clap + response).** Every engagement = follow. No limit.
Article pages have Follow buttons next to the author name. Click → changes to "Following".

```javascript
browser.act({
  kind: "evaluate",
  fn: `() => {
    const btns = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('button'));
    var followBtn = btns.find(b => b.innerText.trim() === 'Follow' && b.getBoundingClientRect().width > 0);
    if (!followBtn) {
      var followingBtn = btns.find(b => b.innerText.trim() === 'Following' && b.getBoundingClientRect().width > 0);
      return { alreadyFollowing: !!followingBtn };
    }
    followBtn.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('click', { bubbles: true, cancelable: true }));
    return { followed: true };
  }`,
  profile: "{{browser_profile}}"
})
```

If `alreadyFollowing`: skip silently. If error: skip follow, proceed.

