## § 7. Check Article Stats

Navigate to `https://medium.com/me/stats`, wait 3s:

```javascript
browser.act({
  kind: "evaluate",
  fn: `() => {
    const table = document.querySelector('table');
    if (!table) return [];
    return Array.from(table.querySelectorAll('tr')).slice(1, 11).map(row => {
      const cells = Array.from(row.querySelectorAll('th, td'));
      return {
        title: cells[0]?.innerText.slice(0, 80),
        views: parseInt(cells[2]?.innerText) || 0,
        reads: parseInt(cells[3]?.innerText) || 0
      };
    });
  }`,
  profile: "{{browser_profile}}"
})
```
